<subSubSection id="0FF4689E550B537F9D0B55143795154D" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" type="method">
<paragraph id="8306C9B7594A3891D4BE59D7F95A5A14" pageId="0" pageNumber="123">Method.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B09117594025A04EA0D8E44C2850A0FB" pageId="0" pageNumber="123">Squash preparations were made on root tips obtained from cultivated plants. Root tips were pre-treated with 0.4% colchicine for 4 h and then fixed in Carnoy solution for 1 h. After hydrolysis in 1N HCl at 60 °C, the tips were stained with leuco-basic fuchsine.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="44B03EB9F732D390B97C0515554C72A5" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" type="observations">
<paragraph id="9ED7D3B5E597D104924EBA948B42AA26" pageId="0" pageNumber="123">Observations.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E8B1DAED0DC9B1275DCBC815AB1C9F84" pageId="0" pageNumber="123">
<taxonomicName id="6042643DFBCE79A7EC7E22B7412F7AA3" authorityName="Guss. (Amaryllidaceae" authorityYear="1827" class="Liliopsida" family="Amaryllidaceae" genus="Allium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Allium permixtum" order="Asparagales" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="permixtum">
<emphasis id="BBD76ABA5AF3C5C2C7B5533E060CD6BC" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="123">Allium permixtum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
occurs in Italy and the Balkan Peninsula (
<bibRefCitation id="E1EF79109240422F44DAEF9ECBFAB43D" author="Anderson, IA" editor="Strid, A" journalOrPublisher="2. Edinburgh University Press, Edinburgh" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" pagination="701 - 714" refId="B1" refString="Anderson, IA, 1991. Allium L. In: Strid, A, Tan, K, Eds., Mountain Flora of Greece Vol. 2. Edinburgh University Press, Edinburgh: 701 - 714" title="Allium L." volumeTitle="Mountain Flora of Greece Vol." year="1991">Anderson 1991</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="225F3325A72A7B7D7B12263645B123EA" author="Conti, F" journalOrPublisher="Almadue srl, Roma" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" refId="B12" refString="Conti, F, 1995. Prodromo della Flora del Parco Nazionale d'Abruzzo. Almadue srl, Roma" title="Prodromo della Flora del Parco Nazionale d'Abruzzo." year="1995">Conti 1995</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="472C7A54D2D1AA835DAD9150478E3B47" author="Cheshmedzhiev, I" journalOrPublisher="Phytologia Balcanica" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" pagination="385 - 388" refId="B9" refString="Cheshmedzhiev, I, Marinov, Y, 2009. Allium phthioticum: new species for the Bulgarian flora. Phytologia Balcanica 15: 385 - 388" title="Allium phthioticum: new species for the Bulgarian flora." volume="15" year="2009">Cheshmedzhiev and Marinov 2009</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="7BDB58FA8D9D69111E7E64B5A6D2E5F2" author="Brullo, C" journalOrPublisher="Pietro Gibelli ed, Bordighera" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" refId="B8" refString="Brullo, C, Brullo, S, Giusso, del Galdo G, 2010. Note tassonomiche e nomenclaturali su Allium permixtum (Alliaceae), specie critica della flora italiana. La Biodiversita vegetale in Italia: aggiornamenti sui gruppi critici della flora vascolare. Societa Botanica Italiana, Roma 22-23 Ottobre: 41-43." title="Note tassonomiche e nomenclaturali su Allium permixtum (Alliaceae), specie critica della flora italiana. La Biodiversita vegetale in Italia: aggiornamenti sui gruppi critici della flora vascolare. Societa Botanica Italiana, Roma 22 - 23 Ottobre: 41 - 43." year="2010">Brullo et al. 2010</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="AAE83B95708804D239DB82667C6A58D2" author="Hallaci, B" journalOrPublisher="3, Edagricole, Bologna" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" refId="B20" refString="Hallaci, B, Shuka, L, 2013. Allium phthioticum Boiss. &amp; Heldr., Allium victorialis L. and Melampyrum bihariense A. Kerner, three new species in the flora of Albania. Natura Montenegrina 12(3-4): 563-568." title="Allium phthioticum Boiss. &amp; Heldr., Allium victorialis L. and Melampyrum bihariense A. Kerner, three new species in the flora of Albania. Natura Montenegrina 12 (3 - 4): 563 - 568." year="2013">
<normalizedToken id="79C1FEC307FC819A8EE6638F26C9B13E" originalValue="Hallaçi">Hallaci</normalizedToken>
and Shuka 2013
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="C3EA1CADC5F403A5EC886F3EC6AE4D01" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1080/11263504.2017.1419996" author="Bartolucci, F" journalOrPublisher="Plant Biosystems" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" pagination="179 - 303" refId="B5" refString="Bartolucci, F, Peruzzi, L, Galasso, G, Albano, A, Alessandrini, A, Ardenghi, NMG, Astuti, G, Bacchetta, G, Ballelli, S, Banfi, E, Barberis, G, Bernardo, L, Bouvet, D, Bovio, M, Cecchi, L, Di Pietro, R, Domina, G, Fascetti, S, Fenu, G, Festi, F, Foggi, B, Gallo, L, Gottschlich, G, Gubellini, L, Iamonico, D, Iberite, M, Jimenez-Mejias, P, Lattanzi, E, Marchetti, D, Martinetto, E, Masin, RR, Medagli, P, Passalacqua, NG, Peccenini, S, Pennesi, R, Pierini, B, Poldini, L, Prosser, F, Raimondo, FM, Roma-Marzio, F, Rosati, L, Santangelo, A, Scoppola, A, Scortegagna, S, Selvaggi, A, Selvi, F, Soldano, A, Stinca, A, Wagensommer, RP, Wilhalm, T, Conti, F, 2018. An updated checklist of the vascular flora native to Italy. Plant Biosystems 152 (2): 179 - 303, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1080/11263504.2017.1419996" title="An updated checklist of the vascular flora native to Italy." url="https://doi.org/10.1080/11263504.2017.1419996" volume="152" year="2018">Bartolucci et al. 2018</bibRefCitation>
). In Italy, this species was not recently confirmed in Sicily (
<bibRefCitation id="D0AFC819566401A50DF252B3A9029B92" author="Brullo, C" journalOrPublisher="Pietro Gibelli ed, Bordighera" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" refId="B8" refString="Brullo, C, Brullo, S, Giusso, del Galdo G, 2010. Note tassonomiche e nomenclaturali su Allium permixtum (Alliaceae), specie critica della flora italiana. La Biodiversita vegetale in Italia: aggiornamenti sui gruppi critici della flora vascolare. Societa Botanica Italiana, Roma 22-23 Ottobre: 41-43." title="Note tassonomiche e nomenclaturali su Allium permixtum (Alliaceae), specie critica della flora italiana. La Biodiversita vegetale in Italia: aggiornamenti sui gruppi critici della flora vascolare. Societa Botanica Italiana, Roma 22 - 23 Ottobre: 41 - 43." year="2010">Brullo et al. 2010</bibRefCitation>
) and is very rare in Abruzzo, where it has been recorded only for some protected areas of the central Apennines, such as the National Park of Gran Sasso and Monti della Laga (
<bibRefCitation id="51A78366A5490E09AB5230FA4EC72A24" author="Conti, F" journalOrPublisher="Bocconea" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" pagination="1 - 276" refId="B13" refString="Conti, F, 1998. An annotated checklist of the flora of the Abruzzo. Bocconea 10: 1 - 276" title="An annotated checklist of the flora of the Abruzzo." volume="10" year="1998">Conti 1998</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="4440A64B66514B910E5F603B0F1E6B60" DOI="https://doi.org/10.11646/phytotaxa.256.1.1" author="Conti, F" journalOrPublisher="Phytotaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" pagination="1 - 119" refId="B15" refString="Conti, F, Bartolucci, F, 2016. The vascular flora of Gran Sasso and Monti della Laga National Park (Central Italy). Phytotaxa 256: 1 - 119, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/phytotaxa.256.1.1" title="The vascular flora of Gran Sasso and Monti della Laga National Park (Central Italy)." url="https://doi.org/10.11646/phytotaxa.256.1.1" volume="256" year="2016">Conti and Bartolucci 2016</bibRefCitation>
) and the National Park of Abruzzo, Lazio and Molise (
<bibRefCitation id="28185370CFF5E018B0A8F2AACF5531DD" author="Conti, F" journalOrPublisher="Almadue srl, Roma" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" refId="B12" refString="Conti, F, 1995. Prodromo della Flora del Parco Nazionale d'Abruzzo. Almadue srl, Roma" title="Prodromo della Flora del Parco Nazionale d'Abruzzo." year="1995">Conti 1995</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="522A8EFD942D2E85FACB7099CA0E36FE" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-319-09701-5" author="Conti, F" journalOrPublisher="Geobotany Studies, Springer International Publishing, Switzerland" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" refId="B14" refString="Conti, F, Bartolucci, F, 2015. The Vascular Flora of the National Park of Abruzzo, Lazio and Molise (Central Italy). An Annotated Checklist. Geobotany Studies, Springer International Publishing, Switzerland, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-319-09701-5" title="The Vascular Flora of the National Park of Abruzzo, Lazio and Molise (Central Italy). An Annotated Checklist." url="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-319-09701-5" year="2015">Conti and Bartolucci 2015</bibRefCitation>
). The population studied here represents the first record for the Regional Park of Sirente-Velino (Abruzzo, central Italy). This is also the first chromosome count for the species in Italy (
